# Arthur Core change

Since the Lancelot API is now truly `getUserById`, update Arthur Core to pass the chosen identifier as `userId`.

For now:

```java
String userId = claims.getPreferredUsername();
UserResponse user = lancelotClient.getUserById(userId);
```

That keeps the API contract right, while the current value happens to be `testuser`.

Later you can switch to:

```java
String userId = claims.getSub();
