# Why this is the best setup

This gives you:

* correct API semantics now
* test data loaded through Liquibase
* no fake `by-username` endpoint
* easy migration later from `preferred_username` to `sub`

So your temporary compromise is only in **Arthur Core claim mapping**, not in the **Lancelot API design**.

